'''Arukas''' tga taɣiwant [[Tigzirin tiknariyin|taknarit]] tlla ɣ ugzzum agafan n [[Tigzirin tiknariyin|Tgzirin Tiknariyin]] ɣ tmnaḍt n Las Palmas. Ilkm uṭṭun n imzdaɣn nns uggar n 36852 n ufgan ɣ usiḍn usggwas 2013. Tiwḍ tjumma n Arakus 33.01 n kilumitr.

Tagwancit tga tantala [[Tutlayin timaziɣin|tamaziɣt]] nna tn kkan ar sawaln imzdaɣn ɣ tɣrmt n Arukas ɣ zikk maca ɣilad tafuḍ s usrag n unkcam n ucngu n [[Ṣbanya|isblyuniyn]].

==Anzwi==
Taskflt n ​​trɣi ɣ tɣrmt n Arukas tiwḍ ɣ uzal ger 21.2 n tskflt d 28° , d 18 n tskflt ɣ yiḍ. ɣ wayyur n innayr ، ar ittawḍ waddad unzwi nns ger 19° d 23° ɣ uzal .

== Asfsr n taysi ==
Asqqim n tɣrmt n Arukas ، ɣ tmnhla n taysi tanmazrayt ɣ Arukas s ddu ufus n umɣnas Manwil Rudrigiz ، skkrn asfsr amaziɣ akanar. iga asfsr n usnɣms ar yssmun tiwlafin n imslitn n ar yttnurẓm tiwwura nns ɣ wass n 15 yunyu ɣ wannar n isfsarn ɣ tgmmi n tdlsa yḍfrn i tɣiwant n Arukas ger wass n aynas ar asimwas ، ɣ tsragt 09.00 d 2:00 tmddit.

